release_note: Thanks for choosing Dust! We re excited to share the next chapter of our journey together. Dust has evolved into a Privacy Security Suite Introducing: Watchdog Type in your email and find out if your info has been compromised in a data breach Introducing: Stealth Search Your first step to privately searching the web A new home experience The new home screen allows you to pick from our suite of privacy products Dusted some bugs that were causing issues.
